---
title: Speedy Chicken Tikka Masala with Green Peas and Basmati Rice
description: This chicken curry is just what we need to warm us up on cool autumn nights. The crunchy green beans are the surprise in every bite! And we guarantee making this dinner will be faster than take-out.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/speedy-chicken-tikka-masala-e8c85657.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/speedy-chicken-tikka-masala-07f272c9.pdf
servings: 2
